These pages describing the housing and industry, both old and new, the people and everyday life in the{Aintree}and{ {Fazakerley}districts of{Liverpool}were contributed by the pupils of the following schools:-
Barlows County Primary School Blessed Sacrament RC Primary School Fazakerley Comprehensive School Holy Name RC Primary School Holy Rosary RC Primary School Longmoor County Primary School Netherton Park County Primary School
Of special interest are items on{ {Aintree Racecourse}, home of the world famous{Grand National Steeplechase}and Liverpool's{Walton Prison.}
